===more:What impressions did Soviet citizens have about life in the United States? What impressions did U.S. citizens have about Soviet life? What parallels do you see between tactics used by the Soviet and U.S. governments to influence public opinion during the Cold War? How did each government try to appeal to the hopes and fears of their citizens?
